item.title: Good P2P items to alch?
item.dc:creator: @bloodrayne bloodrayne
item.description:
@bloodrayne wrote:

Get members and auto click at soul wars

  1. simulate the + key on mousekeys and click twice with no delay between the clicks(alchs one item)

  2. sleep for 600ms+random number between -200,200 ms

  3. loop

Done it on my main for the past few months now after I go to sleep, set computer to turn off 4-5 hours after starting it, effortless ~350k magic experience nightly
